queries.sql: SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb2`.`description` FROM `article_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `article_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "article_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`id` = 12 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`id` desc

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb1`.`image` FROM `product_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `product_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb2`.`module` = "product_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`objectid` = `tb1`.`id` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`level` <= 3 GROUP BY `tb1`.`id` ORDER BY `tb1`.`order` desc, `tb2`.`title`

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc

SELECT `tb4`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`alt`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb2`.`description` as `cat_description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb4`.`image` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`catalogueid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "slide" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`keyword` = 'main-slide' GROUP BY `tb4`.`id`

SELECT `tb4`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`alt`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb2`.`description` as `cat_description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb4`.`image` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`catalogueid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "slide" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`keyword` = 'image-category' GROUP BY `tb4`.`id`

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb1`.`parentid`, `tb1`.`lft`, `tb1`.`rgt`, `tb1`.`level`, `tb1`.`order`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`objectid`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb2`.`catalogueid` as `dataid`, `tb1`.`type` FROM `menu` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `menu_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' ORDER BY `order` desc

SELECT `tb4`.`id`, `tb1`.`keyword`, `tb2`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb3`.`title`, `tb3`.`canonical`, `tb3`.`alt`, `tb3`.`description`, `tb2`.`description` as `cat_description`, `tb3`.`content`, `tb4`.`image` FROM `slide_catalogue` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`module` = "slide_catalogue" AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide_translate` as `tb3` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb3`.`catalogueid` AND `tb3`.`module` = "slide" AND `tb3`.`language` = 'vi' INNER JOIN `slide` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`id` = `tb3`.`objectid` WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`keyword` = 'partner' GROUP BY `tb4`.`id`

SELECT `tb1`.`id`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`module`, `tb1`.`image`, `tb1`.`catalogueid`, `tb2`.`description`, `tb2`.`content`, `tb1`.`userid_created`, `tb1`.`album`, `tb2`.`icon`, `tb1`.`video`, `tb2`.`sub_title`, `tb2`.`sub_content`, `tb2`.`title`, `tb2`.`meta_description`, `tb1`.`created_at`, `tb2`.`canonical`, `tb4`.`title` as `cat_title`, `tb4`.`canonical` as `cat_canonical` FROM `article` as `tb1` INNER JOIN `article_translate` as `tb2` ON `tb1`.`id` = `tb2`.`objectid` AND `tb2`.`language` = 'vi' AND `tb2`.`module` = 'article' INNER JOIN `article_translate` as `tb4` ON `tb4`.`module` = 'article_catalogue' AND `tb1`.`catalogueid` = `tb4`.`objectid` AND `tb4`.`language` = 'vi' WHERE `tb1`.`deleted_at` = 0 AND `tb1`.`publish` = 1 AND `tb1`.`id` IN ('25','23','26','24') ORDER BY `tb1`.`order` desc, `tb1`.`created_at` desc
